	* MonoDevelop.Projects.Parser/PersistentClass.cs: Fix write order.
	* MonoDevelop.Projects.Parser/PersistentMethod.cs: Serialize the body
	region.
	* MonoDevelop.Projects.Parser/CodeCompletionDatabase.cs: Bump db version.

